Twitter Reacts To WWE Smackdown LIVE Seattle Brandon Gnetz Start Slideshow Slide of 
With only five days until Elimination Chamber, Smackdown LIVE delivered another solid two hours of amazing wrestling entertainment that managed to not only build on existing angles, but elevate new stars. 
Heading into the night many groaned over the "first time ever (on Smackdown LIVE)" billing for Orton vs Cena, but an unlikely hero was born in the main event when Luke Harper turned against his old family members. 
The rest of the Elimination Chamber participants lit the night up with a fatal four way and the women's division found a way to make a contract signing feel exciting. 
Here's how Twitter reacted to the night that was in Seattle.
